      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat(ui): add generated image actions",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds first-class generated-image rendering in chat, including image action controls and managed preview/thumbnail handling.\n\n- Adds hover actions for generated/managed images: Open, Download, and Copy.\n- Routes managed generated images through authenticated blob previews so browser image actions work reliably.\n- Retries managed-image preview/action fetches with ordered Control UI auth candidates after `401/403`, so stale read-token credentials do not block owner-capable credentials.\n- Binds requester-session headers to authenticated owner/admin context before serving managed image bytes.\n- Renders generated image frames with stable rounded clipping, known-size geometry, and reserved pending-preview space.\n- Normalizes raw final `MEDIA:` replies before managed media append while keeping Codex callback timeout aligned with the 600000 ms contract.\n- Restacked on current `main` and the clean #75727 head; the previous stale media/trust history is no longer in this PR head.\n- Removed the public `gateway.controlUi.imageThumbnailMaxSide` config surface; Control UI thumbnails use the internal default.\n\n## Why\n\nGenerated images were displayed without the full media affordances expected in chat. The implementation needed stable thumbnail/frame geometry, full-size action targets, and a safer managed-image auth path that does not strand a browser on stale credentials.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n- Current head tested: `89e00c890cd8922295cd9b519914a96273493879`.\n- Behavior addressed: generated/managed chat images render as authenticated thumbnail previews; Open, Download, and Copy are visible browser actions; thumbnail and full-image action fetches retry owner-capable credentials after stale `401/403` credentials; the public thumbnail-size config knob is gone.\n- Real environment tested: exact-head local Linux checkout in a real Chromium browser via Vite using the Control UI source renderer, plus focused gateway/UI/config shards and oxlint.\n\nCommands run after the current fix/proof:\n\n```bash\ngit diff --check\nrg -n \"imageThumbnailMaxSide\" src ui docs -S\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/replay-history.test.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-subscribe.tools.media.test.ts src/config/config-misc.test.ts src/gateway/control-ui.http.test.ts src/gateway/managed-image-attachments.test.ts src/gateway/server-methods/chat.directive-tags.test.ts ui/src/ui/chat/grouped-render.test.ts ui/src/ui/controllers/chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/app-render.helpers.node.test.ts --reporter=verbose\nnode scripts/run-oxlint-shards.mjs --threads=8\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs ui/src/ui/chat/grouped-render.test.ts --reporter=verbose\nnode .artifacts/pr77017-live-proof/run-proof.mjs\n```\n\nLive Chromium image-action evidence:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"head\": \"89e00c890cd8922295cd9b519914a96273493879\",\n  \"readyMarkerVisible\": true,\n  \"imageRenderedFromBlob\": true,\n  \"actionLabels\": [\"Open image\", \"Download image\", \"Copy image\"],\n  \"thumbnailAuthHeaders\": [\"Bearer session-token\", \"Bearer owner-token\"],\n  \"fullAuthHeaders\": [\n    \"Bearer session-token\",\n    \"Bearer owner-token\",\n    \"Bearer session-token\",\n    \"Bearer owner-token\",\n    \"Bearer session-token\",\n    \"Bearer owner-token\"\n  ],\n  \"requesterSessionHeaders\": [\"agent:main:main\"],\n  \"openedUrl\": \"blob:http://127.0.0.1:19890/...\",\n  \"downloadedName\": \"Generated image proof.png\",\n  \"copiedTypes\": [\"image/png\"]\n}\n```\n\nAdditional local evidence:\n\n```text\n$ rg -n \"imageThumbnailMaxSide\" src ui docs -S\n# no matches\n\n$ node scripts/run-vitest.mjs ... --reporter=verbose\n[test] passed 5 Vitest shards in 127.90s\n\n$ node scripts/run-oxlint-shards.mjs --threads=8\n[oxlint:core] finished\n[oxlint:extensions] finished\n[oxlint:scripts] finished\n\n$ node scripts/run-vitest.mjs ui/src/ui/chat/grouped-render.test.ts --reporter=verbose\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  61 passed (61)\n[test] passed 1 Vitest shard in 304.41s\n```\n\nSpecific regression locked in:\n\n- `ui/src/ui/chat/grouped-render.test.ts` verifies managed-image thumbnail and full-image action fetches try `Bearer session-token`, receive `403`, then retry and succeed with `Bearer owner-token` while preserving `x-openclaw-requester-session-key`.\n- `ui/src/ui/app-render.helpers.node.test.ts` verifies ordered unique auth candidates.\n- `src/gateway/control-ui.http.test.ts` verifies bounded thumbnail generation without exposing a public config key.\n\n## Security Impact\n\n- New permissions/capabilities? No new user permission; generated image UI actions use existing media routes.\n- Secrets/tokens handling changed? Yes. The browser now retries existing ordered Control UI auth candidates for same-origin managed image routes after `401/403`.\n- Data access scope changed? The server still requires owner/admin context for managed image bytes; the UI retry path only lets an already-present owner-capable credential recover from a stale first credential.\n\n## Compatibility / Migration\n\n- Backward compatible? Yes.\n- Config/env changes? No. The proposed public thumbnail-size config was removed before merge.\n- Migration needed? No.\n",
        "branch": "forge/ui-managed-image-frame-stability",
